snippet: FIFA will continue to "put pressure" on Qatar about the treatment of migrant laborers building World Cup stadiums in the Gulf Arab country for the 2022 tournament, its President said on Wednesday....
lead_paragraph: FIFA will continue to "put pressure" on Qatar about the treatment of migrant laborers building World Cup stadiums in the Gulf Arab country for the 2022 tournament, its President said on Wednesday.

headline.main: FIFA Will Continue to Put Pressure on Qatar Over Human Rights: President
